sequenceDiagram
    %% ── 图 1: 用户登录后看到公告 + 铃铛角标 ──
    actor User as 用户
    participant Auth as AuthContext
    participant PL as ProtectedLayout
    participant AB as AnnouncementBar
    participant UC as UnreadContext
    participant MB as MessageBell
    participant API as apiClient
    participant Backend as Cloudflare API

    Note over User,Backend: === 图1: 登录后公告 + 铃铛角标初始化 ===

    User->>Auth: login(email, password)
    Auth->>Backend: POST /api/login
    Backend-->>Auth: { token, user }
    Auth->>Auth: setState(isAuthenticated=true)

    Auth-->>PL: 渲染 ProtectedLayout

    par AnnouncementBar 初始化
        PL->>AB: 挂载
        AB->>API: getPublishedAnnouncements()
        API->>Backend: GET /api/announcements
        Backend-->>API: Announcement[]
        API-->>AB: [公告1, 公告2, ...]
        AB->>AB: setState(announcements)
        AB-->>User: 渲染公告横幅（第一条）
    and UnreadContext 初始化
        PL->>UC: 挂载 UnreadProvider
        UC->>API: getUnreadCount()
        API->>Backend: GET /api/messages/unread-count
        Backend-->>API: { count: 3 }
        API-->>UC: 3
        UC->>UC: setState(unreadCount=3)
    and MessageBell 渲染
        PL->>MB: 挂载（Header 内）
        MB->>UC: 消费 unreadCount
        UC-->>MB: unreadCount=3
        MB-->>User: 渲染铃铛 + 红色角标 "3"
    end

    UC->>UC: 启动 60s 轮询定时器

    Note over UC: 页面隐藏时暂停轮询<br/>document.visibilitychange

    %% ── 图 2: 用户点击铃铛 → 查看消息 → 标记已读 ──

    Note over User,Backend: === 图2: 铃铛 → 消息列表 → 标记已读 ===

    User->>MB: 点击铃铛
    MB->>MB: navigate('/messages')

    User->>MP: MessagesPage 挂载
    MP->>API: getMyMessages()
    API->>Backend: GET /api/messages
    Backend-->>API: Message[]
    API-->>MP: [msg1(unread), msg2(read), ...]
    MP->>MP: setState(messages, loading=false)
    MP-->>User: 渲染消息列表<br/>未读加粗+蓝点，已读灰色

    User->>MP: 点击未读消息 msg1
    MP->>MP: setState(expandedId=msg1.id)
    MP->>API: markMessageRead(msg1.id)
    API->>Backend: PUT /api/messages/1/read
    Backend-->>API: { code: 0 }

    par 更新消息状态
        MP->>MP: setState(messages: msg1.isRead=1)
        MP-->>User: 消息变灰，移除加粗
    and 更新未读计数
        MP->>UC: setUnreadCount(prev => prev - 1)
        UC->>UC: unreadCount: 3 → 2
        UC-->>MB: 重新渲染
        MB-->>User: 角标 "3" → "2"
    end
